&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accommodations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;Samsara is an inclusive work environment, and we are committed to ensuring equal opportunity in employment for qualified persons with disabilities. Please email &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="mailto:accessibleinterviewing@samsara.com"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;accessibleinterviewing@samsara.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt; or &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://form.asana.com/?k=dcecpJYeVpOJt1RCCU7Hdg&amp;amp;d=182866037607514"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;click here&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt; if you require any reasonable accommodations throughout the recruiting process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
