&lt;h2 class="Header-module__header--zowtw"&gt;💛 EOE&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whatnot is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer. We value diversity, and we do not discriminate on the basis of race, religion, color, national origin, gender, sexual orientation, age, marital status, veteran status, parental status, disability status, or any other status protected by local law. We believe that our work is better and our company culture is improved when we encourage, support, and respect the different skills and experiences represented within our workforce.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;About Us&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Twitch is the world's biggest live streaming service, with global communities built around gaming, entertainment, music, sports, cooking, and more. It is where thousands of communities come together for whatever, every day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We're about community, inside and out. You'll find coworkers who are eager to team up, collaborate, and smash (or elegantly solve) problems together. We're on a quest to empower live communities, so if this sounds good to you, see what we're up to on &lt;a href="https://link.twitch.tv/TwitchLinkedinJD"&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://link.twitch.tv/TwitchTwitterJD"&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;, and discover the projects we're solving on our &lt;a href="https://link.twitch.tv/TwitchBlogJD"&gt;Blog&lt;/a&gt;. Be sure to explore our &lt;a href="https://link.twitch.tv/TwitchInterviewingJD"&gt;Interviewing Guide&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://link.twitch.tv/TwitchInstagramJD"&gt;Instagram&lt;/a&gt; channel to learn how to ace our interview process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;About the Role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Twitch FinTech owns the portfolio of financial systems that support Twitch’s finance, accounting, and tax operations. Currently, we are going through a multi-year business transformation program enabled with implementation of SAP S/4HANA and Coupa. As our SAP ABAP Technical lead, you will report to our Head of FinTech. We're open to candidates working from Seattle, WA, Los Angeles, CA, or remote anywhere in the United States.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;You Will:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Play the role of SAP ABAP technical lead, part of Twitch's FinTech team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage technical design and custom developments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure adherence to the coding standards, perform code reviews, ensure adequate documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with partners, engineering teams, and with onsite/ offshore resources from SI partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive E2E technical solutions in collaboration with middleware, engineering and other IT teams within Twitch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with PMO to ensure delivery of critical project milestones&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously evaluate and refine solutions to ensure they are efficient, high quality, agile and scalable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;You Have:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years of experience in implementation of SAP systems; at least 3 years of experience in S/4HANA&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience in technical coding in SAP S/4HANA (ABAP, UI5) for custom RICEFW developments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently to accomplish the tasks and duties assigned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Built integrations between SAP and non-SAP systems, including Coupa and Tableau&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in different integration techniques - e.g. File-based, Web Services, SOAP and REST-based API's, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep knowledge in HANA data modeling, HANA optimized coding, embedded analytics, Fiori App extensions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Played technical lead role in SAP implementation programs; managed onsite and offshore development teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience using various project management tools like AirTable, Smartsheet, Lucidchart, or JIRA&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Bonus Points&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in BRIM, FICA, RAR is nice to have&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Techno-Functional, with functional experience in the realm of finance, order-to-cash, and procurement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A team-oriented and collaborative attitude with the ability to foster cooperation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in digital content/ media industry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Perks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medical, Dental, Vision &amp;amp; Disability Insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401(k)&lt;/li&gt;
