&lt;li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="11" data-aria-posinset="5" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;span data-contrast="auto"&gt;The ability to make a real impact in an incredibly fast-growing organization; you’ll never be just another cog in the wheel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;134233279&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
