&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;$50-$60/hr&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Upon successful completion, this candidate would be eligible for a $5,000 completion bonus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class="content-conclusion"&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Flatiron School&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
