&lt;div class="content-intro"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Remote&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Remote is solving global remote organizations’ biggest challenge: employing anyone anywhere compliantly. We make it possible for businesses big and small to employ a global team by handling global payroll, benefits, taxes, and compliance. Check out &lt;a href="http://remote.com/how-it-works"&gt;remote.com/how-it-works&lt;/a&gt; to learn more or if you’re interested in adding to the mission, scroll down to apply now.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please take a look at &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="http://remote.com/handbook"&gt;remote.com/handbook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; to learn more about our culture and what it is like to work here. &lt;strong&gt;Not only do we encourage folks from all ethnic groups, genders, sexuality, age and abilities to apply, but we prioritize a sense of &lt;a href="https://www.notion.so/people-Belonging-Diversity-Equity-Inclusion-DEI-4990e36a7d7b4d52a78ca3efb23d718b"&gt;belonging&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt; You can check out independent reviews by other candidates on &lt;a href="https://www.glassdoor.com/Overview/Working-at-Remote-EI_IE3871683.11,17.htm"&gt;Glassdoor&lt;/a&gt; or look up the &lt;a href="https://www.notion.so/people-Candidate-Experience-Surveys-17d595a88b7548148593792a8072235f"&gt;results of our candidate surveys&lt;/a&gt; to see how others feel about working and interviewing here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All of our positions are fully remote. You do not have to relocate to join us!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What this job can offer you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will have the opportunity to gain additional expertise in Global Benefits Operations. You can check&amp;nbsp;the 70+ countries in which we already operate &lt;a href="https://remote.com/countries"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will manage customer and employee queries for multiple countries with a customer-centric approach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will be responsible for managing all aspects of the benefits processes for your group of plans across multiple countries from start to finish&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will design processes, manage data, support product design and manage invoices for your assigned group of global benefits plans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will work closely with the Benefits Solutions team to improve and update existing benefits plans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a &lt;a href="https://signalvnoise.com/posts/1430-hire-managers-of-one"&gt;manager of one&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have previous experience in managing global Benefits/HR Operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You thrive working in a fast-paced environment and multi-task effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are tech-savy and proactive in leveraging new tools and technologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are motivated by providing an excellent customer service experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are able to propose, innovate and challenge the status quo&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Practicals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll report to:&lt;/strong&gt; Benefits Manager&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Direct reports:&lt;/strong&gt; None&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team:&lt;/strong&gt; Benefits Operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;: You need to be in the timezone in EMEA (UTC +3 to UTC +4) as the team needs the coverage in the timezone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Start date:&lt;/strong&gt; As soon as possible&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Remote Compensation Philosophy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Remote's &lt;a href="https://www.notion.so/people-Total-Rewards-1945bce8d3924ece9421ba8630f57b0c?pvs=21"&gt;Total Rewards philosophy&lt;/a&gt; is to ensure fair, unbiased compensation and fair equity pay along with competitive benefits in all locations in which we operate. We do not agree to or encourage cheap-labor practices and therefore we ensure to pay above in-location rates. We hope to inspire other companies to support global talent-hiring and bring local wealth to developing countries.&lt;/p&gt;
