&lt;p&gt;Roughly 4 hours across 6 weeks&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interview with Manager&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interview with Senior manager&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interview with VP of Benefits&lt;/li&gt;
